{
  "stem": "10446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One event made it very clear, finally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was accused of Rassenschande, having a relationship with a Gentile woman, which was a completely trumped-up charge.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was taken to the concentration camp of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was in 1937.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hella and I had just gotten married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in those days, it was still possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People still got out of, of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was there for about a week, four, five days, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hella and I, we drove to Munich where the headquarters of the Nazi, of SS, the Stormtroopers, was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we spoke to somebody there in full uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In later years, all this would have been impossible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we pleaded our case and succeeded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After about four or five days, my father was let go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That this must be an error.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would like to know who accused him of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we tried to prove it couldn't be possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had witnesses who did testify that this was most, almost impossible, because this was a village down in the country, and everybody would have known what was going on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they finally let him go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He never said one word about his experiences at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not one word.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just kept silent about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said, in those days, we knew several other men who were taken to Dachau and, and set free again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on, that became a different story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're not sure when we met first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was probably on a tennis court in Nuremberg, and-- but didn't pay much attention, much attention to each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We finally got to know us better on a vacation where my wife was together with friends, with her father as a chaperone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was at the University of Munich at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
